{
  "texts": [
    "And as he entered the city gates, the people recognized him and gathered to hear him speak.",
    "6 Jonah called out with a loud voice, \"People of Nineveh, forty days from now, Nineveh will be destroyed if you do not repent.\"",
    "7 The people wailed and put on sackcloth, from the greatest to the least.",
    "Even the king rose from his throne, removed his royal robes, covered himself in ashes, and sat on the ground.",
    "8 A decree went out: \"By order of the king: No person or animal may eat or drink."
  ]
}